What is an action?

- Actions are the simplest version of a Task there is.
- Actions have one purpose only, and may consist of 1 to many stages of execution, just like normal tasks.
- Actions are not submitted to the Task Manager however, they must be joined with other actions into Tasks or explicitly
    converted to one.
- Actions can be performed (through urgent queue manipulation) instantly via the bot menu to test the action.
- Each action has set